Package cscie97.asn4.ecommerce.collection

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICollectionServiceAPI
    Public interface for the CollectionServiceAPI.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Collectible
    Abstract parent class for Collection and ContentProxy objects.
    Collection
    Abstract class for Collections.
    CollectionIterator
    Allows for the iteration of Collectible items.
    CollectionServiceAPI
    Implements the ICollectionServiceAPI class to provide public methods for interaction with the Collection catalog.
    ContentProxy
    Wrapper class for Content objects that may be contained in Collections.
    DynamicCollection
    DynamicCollections contain a ContentSearch object which is executed upon defining the ContentSearch.
    StaticCollection
    Marker class for StaticCollections.
